resolveMe

private java.util.Collection<Study> resolveMe(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,Study> studies,
                                              ListAllResponse allStudies)
                                       throws ODMException,
                                              OCConnectorException,
                                              javax.xml.datatype.DatatypeConfigurationException
This is where all the logic sits for resolving ODM data. ODM data is processed here and unresolved attributes are resolved, subjects are created, events are scheduled... This method operated on a pre-fetched LastAllResponse object.

Parameters:
studies - internal study data (our cache)
allStudies - all studies from listAll OpenClinica method.
Returns:
A collection of studies.
Throws:
ODMException
OCConnectorException
javax.xml.datatype.DatatypeConfigurationException
